    <h3><u>Our Story</u>:</h3>
    <h4>Northern Threads is a Canadian-based store for top of the line business attire. Established in
      2017, we have quickly grown to become Canada's most respected brand of formal wear. Our brand is
      what helps make our country strive to be the greatest. Unlike some competitors, we bleed authenticity.
      What you see is what you get with our impeccably designed and created clothing.
    </h4>
  </div>
