  <div id="Guarantee">
      <h3><u>Our Guarantee</u>:</h3>
      <h4>We stand 100% behind our products here at Northern Threads and guarantee that if for any 
        reason you are not fully satisfied with your purchase, you can definitely send it back to us. 
        We honor full refunds and exchanges for the original price paid, given that it is within the
        time period as indicated on your proof of purchase. As well, if anything you receive is damaged 
        or not quite the item you ordered, you may send it back to us for free.
      </h4>
  </div>
